    <item>
      <title>美国 6 月份核心 PCE 上涨 0.2%，支出保持坚挺</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-07-26/us-core-pce-rises-0-2-in-june-personal-spending-remains-firm</link>
      <description><![CDATA[核心个人消费支出价格指数是美联储衡量潜在通胀的首选指标，6 月份该指数上涨 0.2%，较上年同期上涨 2.6%。迈克尔·麦基在彭博电视台上对这些数字进行了详细分析。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-07-26/us-core-pce-rises-0-2-in-june-personal-spending-remains-firm</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 26 Jul 2024 13:03:53 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>日元“疯狂”涨势可能最早下周就破灭</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-26/-crazy-yen-rally-is-at-risk-of-shattering-as-soon-as-next-week</link>
      <description><![CDATA[近几周，投资者纷纷买入日元，押注利率最终将向有利于日本的方向倾斜。他们最早将在周三面临关键时刻。]]></description>
